{"tid":124422,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔同人生階段會鍾意聽beyond唔同嘅歌？","createTime":"2017-02-17T14:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T17:52:03.000Z","uid":64183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65394b1e0a18cb03870497d026d66c7c6fe29812","tid":124422,"uid":64183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"小弟唔敢認係資深beyond，都係聽開大路野<br />\n小學初初接觸因爲今天我同光輝歲月愛上beyond<br />\n去大學階段迷上冷雨夜早班火車等等，感受果種惆悵<br />\n到而家做緊野就狂loop灰色軌跡誰伴我闖蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e3c20fb1a30f449564c2f588f16c7f01b80ce6","tid":124422,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"Forever beyond"},{"pid":"96d132b001bc906fc1770987106c6109063381a4","tid":124422,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:29:13.000Z","msg":"我係咁loop 不再猶豫，無悔這一生同光輝歲月<br />\n利申 : Beyond fans"},{"pid":"ccd17938cb288ca9765b59de3e20bdb1b8449fa5","tid":124422,"uid":12521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"今天我"},{"pid":"a2d2089ae614cb9842538b7dc4b09c08cc4a2968","tid":124422,"uid":64183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係咁loop 不再猶豫，無悔這一生同光輝歲月<br />\n利申 : Beyond fans</blockquote><br />\n巴打聽得好正面"},{"pid":"76d748642a0407b33b03c1fb0d83987423f92278","tid":124422,"uid":58392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"冷門推介：又是黃昏<br />\n唔好聽小島版本，一定要聽家駒唱<br />\n<br />\n中學生個陣聽冇乜特別，大個左聽真係唱入心坎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋曲風算係特別小小，好想有多d哩類作品，可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72f54450a99da4389a113ab537f2e21670d539f","tid":124422,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"再見理想最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (家駒獨唱個version)<br />\n<br />\n一聽到開波guitar solo個bend線已經起哂雞皮<br />\n每一段歌詞就好似一個情境咁,chorus果段正正描寫緊當時beyond每個人嘅心聲<br />\n中段個guitar solo更係蕩氣回腸,畫龍點睛<br />\n家駒唏噓嘅歌聲真係百聽不厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCTdbCdAFjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjCTdbCdAFjc&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2997c339\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCTdbCdAFjc</a><br />\n1986年cd版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Kjd-bLojis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_Kjd-bLojis&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ff88d39e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Kjd-bLojis</a><br />\n1991年紅館live<br />\n<br />\nbtw五子時期玩d rock/punk野都好正,同四子主打pop都係各有千秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三子時期冇留意了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a21bbe3c0705c4c69fa9c521213d7ac02c02506","tid":124422,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係咁loop 不再猶豫，無悔這一生同光輝歲月<br />\n利申 : Beyond fans</blockquote><br />\n巴打聽得好正面</blockquote><br />\n可能我而家係求學階段   每次成績考得唔滿意我都會聽  提自己唔好懶散  發奮圖強"},{"pid":"04006740eced6137ac293dccb317bd4a05b0a547","tid":124422,"uid":58392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再見理想最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (家駒獨唱個version)<br />\n<br />\n一聽到開波guitar solo個bend線已經起哂雞皮<br />\n每一段歌詞就好似一個情境咁,chorus果段正正描寫緊當時beyond每個人嘅心聲<br />\n中段個guitar solo更係蕩氣回腸,畫龍點睛<br />\n家駒唏噓嘅歌聲真係百聽不厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCTdbCdAFjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjCTdbCdAFjc&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2997c339\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCTdbCdAFjc</a><br />\n1986年cd版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Kjd-bLojis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_Kjd-bLojis&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ff88d39e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Kjd-bLojis</a><br />\n1991年紅館live<br />\n<br />\nbtw五子時期玩d rock/punk野都好正,同四子主打pop都係各有千秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三子時期冇留意了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三子時期其實都有驚喜，幾鐘意不見不散"},{"pid":"a1151435a7f22277c3a0d5cc55d174e712a74acb","tid":124422,"uid":16812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"早班火車forever"}]}